    esp_timer_delete(timer_handle);
    timer_handle = nullptr;
}
```

This prevents invalid accesses during teardown and conforms with ESP-IDF best practices.

---

#### 3. Thread Safety via Mutex Locking
All public methods interacting with shared hardware/state should use a mutex to prevent race conditions:

